OL,3,CMore than half of Universal Credit
OL,4,Cclaimants ran out of food last month
OL,6,FMore than half of people in the South
OL,7,FEast who receive Universal Credit, ran
OL,8,Fout of food last month, and couldn't
OL,9,Fafford any more.
OL,11,FThat's according to the anti-poverty
OL,12,Fcharity the Trussell Trust - which is
OL,13,Fcalling on the Government to take
OL,14,Faction.
