OL,3,CMore than half of Universal Credit
OL,4,Cclaimants ran out of food last month
OL,6,FIt says more than 88,000 people
OL,7,Fclaiming the benefit, needed a food
OL,8,Fbank within the last month, and more
OL,9,Fthan 62% of those people are either
OL,10,Fbehind on bills and credit commitments
OL,11,For are finding it a constant struggle
OL,12,Fto keep up with them.
OL,14,FThe Trust is urging the Chancellor to
OL,15,Ftake urgent action to increase long-
OL,16,Fterm support for people struggling to
OL,17,Fget by on Universal Credit and commit
OL,18,Fto extending the Household Support
OL,19,FFund as soon as possible.
