OL,3,CMore than half of Universal Credit
OL,4,Cclaimants ran out of food last month
OL,6,FIt says though temporary measures such
OL,7,Fas the cost of living payments have
OL,8,Fhelped people on the lowest incomes in
OL,9,Fthe short term, they have only
OL,10,Fprovided short-term respite, and a
OL,11,Fmore permanent solution urgently needs
OL,12,Fto be put in place.
