OL,3,CMore than half of Universal Credit
OL,4,Cclaimants ran out of food last month
OL,6,FEmma Revie, Chief Executive of the
OL,7,FTrussell Trust, said: "This research
OL,8,Femphasises the stark truth about
OL,9,Fpoverty across the UK and the
OL,10,Fgovernment cannot stand by and let
OL,11,Fthis continue. They must act now to
OL,12,Fimplement permanent solutions that
OL,13,Falleviate the hardship faced by so
OL,14,Fmany and prevent people from
OL,15,Fspiralling deeper into poverty.
