OL,6,F"Food banks do all they can to support
OL,7,Fpeople in their communities, but
OL,8,Fcharities alone can't take the place
OL,9,Fof a social security system that
OL,10,Fshould support any of us who have
OL,11,Ffallen on hard times and need help.
OL,13,F"The Chancellor must commit to
OL,14,Fextending the Household Support Fund
OL,15,Fas part of the Spring Budget, which
OL,16,Fhas provided a lifeline for so many
OL,17,Fpeople. Cutting off the funding in
OL,18,FMarch would leave a huge gap in
OL,19,Fsupport that neither councils nor
OL,20,Fcharities can fill.
