OL,6,F"Alongside this, the government must
OL,7,Fact now to introduce an Essentials
OL,8,FGuarantee, ensuring social security
OL,9,Fprovides a protected minimum amount of
OL,10,Fsupport so that people can always
OL,11,Fafford the essentials, such as food
OL,12,Fand household bills.
