OL,6,F"We know that the public is deeply
OL,7,Fconcerned about poverty and hunger,
OL,8,Fwith 72% supporting our call for an
OL,9,FEssentials Guarantee and tens of
OL,10,Fthousands already having signed our
OL,11,Fpetition calling for an Essentials
OL,12,FGuarantee. We encourage anyone who
OL,13,Fbelieves that Universal Credit should
OL,14,Falways protect people from going
OL,15,Fwithout the essentials to join them.
