OL,6,F"Every member of the UK Parliament has
OL,7,Fto take responsibility for making the
OL,8,Fchanges needed to tackle poverty and
OL,9,Fto bring about the changes required to
OL,10,Fmove towards ending the need for food
OL,11,Fbanks, for good."
OL,13,FCass Francis, Southend Foodbank, said:
OL,14,F"Every day in our food bank we see
OL,15,Fproof that the 'cost of living' crisis
OL,16,Fisn't over. We've seen foodbank use
OL,17,Fincrease exponentially in the ten
OL,18,Fyears we've been open, and there are
OL,19,Fno signs of it slowing.
